  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 18th level, you gain preternatural senses that help you fight creatures you can't see. When you attack a creature you can't see, your inability to see it doesn't impose <strong>disadvantage </strong>on your attack rolls against it.</p>\n<p>You are also aware of the location of any invisible creature within 30 feet of you, provided that the creature isn't hidden from you and you aren't <strong>blinded </strong>or <strong>deafened</strong>.</p>",
